Data and third-party materials
==============================

BEAR is a compilation of third-party datasets described in doc/datasets.Rmd.
Those datasets are governed by their original licenses (e.g., CC BY 4.0,
CC BY-NC 4.0, CC0 1.0 Universal, public domain, GPL-3, or other terms noted in
that document). This repository does not grant rights to reuse third-party
data beyond the permissions of the original sources. Users must comply with
those upstream licenses and attribution requirements when using any dataset
or derived artifacts (including releases such as BEAR.rds).
